{"tid":830591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當庭驗鳥揭性侵2女　鬼父判20年疑畏罪自縊亡 正圖","createTime":"2018-09-21T09:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T09:46:18.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0d974d28bb1e97d446b19a7b10bdf632ee2929a7","tid":830591,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T09:32:58.000Z","msg":"判決指出，林男（45歲）性侵兩個女兒共7次，被害人分為林男與第一任妻子親生、第二任妻子與前夫所生。林男先於2007年間性侵當時僅13歲的親生女兒，被害人滿14歲後，2008年6月到2010年間，又遭林男性侵3次。<br />\n林男與第一任妻子離婚不久，隨即再娶第二任妻子，女方帶著與前夫所生的女兒同住，林男卻在2012年9月到2013年12月，性侵當時僅16歲的繼女共3次。事發後，林始終否認犯罪，推稱女兒指控不可信，但繼女指述林男下體頂端有1顆痣，法官命法醫當庭勘驗屬實。<br />\n此外，林男的親生女兒與繼女都出現遭受性侵害所產生的創傷後壓力症狀，法官認為女孩所述的事實較可信，一、二審均依6個強制性交罪各判刑6年、1個加重強制性交罪判刑8年，合併應執行20年徒刑，最高法院今年8月9日駁回上訴，維持原判決定讞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180921/1434209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180921%2F1434209&d=UPo%2BapQ%2FltICJJmezQhqlYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=65772123\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180921%2F1434209&h=27d4d3a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180921/1434209</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180921/640_52fd022222d3cdf8e08d19a5e51158d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180921%2F640_52fd022222d3cdf8e08d19a5e51158d8.jpg&h=5cbfb9b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0b6c2451e2243813cfb893f041472265971bf51","tid":830591,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T09:33:44.000Z","msg":"正圖係咩意思？"},{"pid":"b1c7be613afcf0cf8bd75b89370ae39bc5c970ef","tid":830591,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0b6c2451e2243813cfb893f041472265971bf51","tid":830591,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T09:33:44.000Z","msg":"正圖係咩意思？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-